Eurasia
-------
[3] Russia (Khanty-Mansi Autonomous Okrug ex Dagestan)
Date: Thu 7 Aug 2014
Source: Ostrana.ru [in Russian, machine trans., edited]
http://ostrana.ru/news/topic/v_yugru_zavezli_kor_iz_dagestana


In the Nizhnevartovsk district of KhMAO [Khanty-Mansi Autonomous Okrug, also known as Yugra] a diagnosis of "measles" has been confirmed in 8 local residents. Local physicians have established that the disease was brought to Nizhnevartovsk by a local man who had spent his vacation in the Republic of Dagestan with his family. The 1st cases were members of his family followed by colleagues.

Currently there are now 6 confirmed cases, including one child in hospital. The condition of 2 other cases has improved and they have been discharged from hospital. All of the cases exhibited moderately severe illness. The entire population of population of the District has now been vaccinated.

--
